name: YunXi 云曦 完美世界_waichi
description:
我會把這個模型公開展示出來，目的是測試、學術研究和討論用。

熱烈歡迎您在這裡與我交流改進空間，如果您有任何建議，請隨時在下面發表評論。用戶在使用本模型時，請務必遵守當地法律法規。

若此模型侵犯了您的權利，請聯繫我，將會下架處理。

你可以在我的 patreon 上支持我，也可以在上面許願你想要我訓練的模型，將為你服務~

I will present this model publicly for testing, academic research and discussion purposes.

I hope to discuss training methods with you. You are warmly welcome to communicate with me about room for improvement here, and if you have any suggestions, please feel free to leave a comment below.

When using this model, users must abide by local laws and regulations.

If this model violates your rights, please contact me and it will be removed from the shelves.

You can support me on my patreon, there you can also make a wish which model you want me to train, will serve you~

Tips:

• It is recommended to use Trigger Words (LiuShen) in the prompt.

• The best result of using this Lora alone is around 0.75~1.0.

• This model works best in GuoFeng, PerfectWorld others you can try.
